Common¶

Common ML operations to be used by all algorithms in POM3.

class MMLL.models.POM3.CommonML.POM3_CommonML.POM3_CommonML_Master(comms, logger, verbose=False)¶

Bases: MMLL.models.Common_to_POMs_123.Common_to_POMs_123_Master

This class implements the Common ML operations, run at Master node. It inherits from Common_to_POMs_123_Master.

Create a POM3_CommonML_Master instance.

Parameters

  • comms (Comms_master) – Object providing communications functionalities.

  • logger (mylogging.Logger) – Logging object instance.

  • verbose (boolean) – Indicates whether to print messages on screen nor not.

Init_Environment()¶

This is the main initialization loop, it runs the following actions until the stop condition is met:

  • Update the execution state.

  • Perform actions according to the state.

  • Process the received packets.

None –

transform_encrypted_domain_workers(encrypted_data, worker_origin, worker_destination, verbose=True)¶

Function to transform encrypted data from domain of worker_origin to worker_destination.

Parameters

  • encrypted_data (list of arrays) – Encrypted data using public key of worker_origin.

  • worker_origin (int) – Index of the worker who encrypted the data.

  • worker_destination (int) – Index of the worker to transform the encrypted data to.

Returns
